lyrics:
[Verse]
Isaiah's from the mountains, Elizabeth from the coast
Two hearts so distant, but love was destined to grow
Different worlds they come from, but fate has brought them near
Their love's like the sunrise, chasing away all fear

[Chorus]
Isaiah and Elizabeth, a love so pure and true
Crossing oceans and borders, destiny brought them through
Hand in hand, they'll face the world, whatever may unfurl
Their love knows no boundaries, forever they'll be twirled
